#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.45"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.45:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.45:0.2"
msgid "5. Attadīpavagga"
msgstr "5. Be Your Own Island"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 45. Aniccasutta → paṭhamaaniccatāsuttaṃ (bj) | aniccatā 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.45:0.3"
msgid "45. Aniccasutta"
msgstr "45. Impermanence"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.45"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.45:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is impermanent."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.3"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ;"
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.4"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā;"
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.5"
msgid ""
"yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And what’s not-self should be truly seen with proper understanding like this:"
" ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’"

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passato cittaṃ virajjati vimuccati "
"anupādāya āsavehi."
msgstr ""
"Seeing truly with right understanding like this, the mind becomes "
"dispassionate and freed from defilements by not grasping."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.7"
msgid "Vedanā aniccā …"
msgstr "Feeling is impermanent …"

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.8"
msgid "saññā …"
msgstr "Perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.9"
msgid "saṅkhārā …"
msgstr "Choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.10"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ."
msgstr "Consciousness is impermanent."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.11"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ;"
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.12"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā;"
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.13"
msgid ""
"yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And what’s not-self should be truly seen with proper understanding like this:"
" ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’"

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.14"
msgid ""
"Evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passato cittaṃ virajjati vimuccati "
"anupādāya āsavehi."
msgstr ""
"Seeing truly with right understanding like this, the mind becomes "
"dispassionate and freed from defilements by not grasping."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.15"
msgid ""
"Rūpadhātuyā ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno cittaṃ virattaṃ vimuttaṃ hoti anupādāya "
"āsavehi, vedanādhātuyā … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If a mendicant’s mind is dispassionate towards the form element, the feeling "
"element,"

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.16"
msgid "saññādhātuyā …"
msgstr "the perception element,"

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.17"
msgid "saṅkhāradhātuyā …"
msgstr "the choices element,"

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.18"
msgid ""
"viññāṇadhātuyā ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno cittaṃ virattaṃ vimuttaṃ hoti "
"anupādāya āsavehi."
msgstr ""
"and the consciousness element, it’s freed from defilements by not grasping."

#. VAR: santusitaṃ → santussitaṃ (si, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn22.45:1.19"
msgid ""
"Vimuttattā ṭhitaṃ. Ṭhitattā santusitaṃ. Santusitattā na paritassati. "
"Aparitassaṃ paccattaññeva parinibbāyati."
msgstr ""
"Being free, it’s stable. Being stable, it’s content. Being content, they’re "
"not anxious. Not being anxious, they personally become extinguished."

msgctxt "sn22.45:1.20"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānātī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.45:1.21"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
